---
USA Virgin Islands. 28 Jul 2017. (conf.) 1st case of Zika-related microcephaly.
http://viconsortium.com/health/17-additional-pregnant-woman-infected-with-zika-d-o-h-s-latest-report-shows-bringing-total-to-271/

